  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">Edit | Application-Settings</para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_" style="page-break-before:always;">Application Settings</para>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_"><text styleclass="VariableName">Application Settings</text><text styleclass="Body Text"> include: </text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo">colors, number-formats, element sizes, ... and</text><text styleclass="B Bullets"> many more settings.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Heading4 Toggle_atocs_">To open the Application-Setting dialog:</para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="2" colcount="2">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:32px; border-bottom:none;">
          <para styleclass="Image Caption"><image src="MD-Icon-ApplicationSettings.png" scale="100.00%" figurelistinclude="0"></image></para>
        </td>
        <td style="vertical-align:middle; border-bottom:none;">
          <para styleclass="B Bullets"><text styleclass="T_Menu">Edit toolbar &gt; Application-Settings</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td style="width:32px; border-top:none;">
          <para styleclass="Body Text" style="text-align:center;">or</para>
        </td>
        <td style="vertical-align:middle; border-top:none;">
          <para styleclass="B Bullets"><text styleclass="T_Menu">Edit menu &gt; Edit Application-Settings</text></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">The <text styleclass="Interface">Application-Settings dialog</text> is now open.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="SeeAlso">See <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-Application-Settings">Application-Settings dialog</link>&#32;</para>
    <para styleclass="SeeAlso">See also: <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Edit-MachineSettings">Machine-Settings dialog</link> &#160;</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="VariableName"><text styleclass="Notes">Notes</text><text styleclass="Body Text">: </text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo">We save your <text styleclass="VariableName">Application-Settings</text> automatically for you when you exit <text styleclass="VariableName">MechDesigner</text> to these files:</para>
    <list id="0" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Body Text HowTo" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="VariableName">&lt;LocalAppData&gt;\IniFiles\MechDesigner.INI</text>&#32;</li>
      <li styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="VariableName">&lt;LocalAppData&gt;\IniFiles\ MechDesigner.XML</text>&#32;</li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text">Delete these two files</text> to revert to factory-settings.</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#343400;" /></para>
  </body>
